      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented software quality assurance programs including version control, regression testing, and change management consistent with ASME V&V 40 gradation 3 requirements."
    },
    {
