      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be sufficiently similar to the intended use scenario to support extrapolation of credibility evidence.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the ASTM F1717 standardized test used in the regulatory submission. Specimen geometry, material, and loading protocol are identical between validation and intended use scenario, supporting full relevance at gradation 3."
