    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is accepted given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol context and multi-laboratory experimental replication. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory claim.",
